Uses of Package
org.anyframe.query

Packages that use org.anyframe.query
org.anyframe.query Provides interface for executing SQL queries or updates, initiating iteration over ResultSets And also provides exception class that is thrown when there is any problem executing the query 
org.anyframe.query.config   
org.anyframe.query.dao Convenient super class for QueryService. 
org.anyframe.query.impl Provides implementation class for QueryService interface and also provides paging classes 
org.anyframe.query.impl.config.loader Provides classes to load mapping xml file information 
org.anyframe.query.impl.jdbc Provides extend classes from Spring's JdbcTemplate 
org.anyframe.query.impl.jdbc.mapper   
org.anyframe.query.impl.jdbc.setter
